I just bought the semiconductor ETF, SOXX because semiconductors as a whole seem like a winner, while a few here and there might be losers in the short-medium term (looking at you Intel). Includes everything from the tooling guys like KLA and ASML to the fabs like TSM and the chip designers like Nvidia.

&amp;#x200B;

If you want an even higher weighting of the up comers like Nvidia, TSMC, and SMD, check out SMH.

